Package org.moddingx.libx.util.data

Class TagAccess

java.lang.Object
org.moddingx.libx.util.data.TagAccess
public class TagAccess extends Object
A class to help accessing tags in a more user friendly way. A TagAccess can contain a RegistryAccess to allow accessing dynamic registries.
